snippet.title: Turnabout of Courage [FT] Part 1: It's Usually The Butz
snippet.description:
[A Visual Novelty First-Time Playthrough]

This is the fancase that I mentioned at the end of Amusement and Turnabout.. It's been kinda on my list ever since it was brought to my attention that the BG watermark errors were fixed!

On that note, Larry Butz's spooky test of courage begins! What could possibly go wrong at midnight in an abandoned church?
-------------------
Fangame by Blackrune!
Play it on AA Online starting here! http://www.aaonline.fr/player.php?trial_id=27826

Watch more fangames from me! https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLaW1SKhhC603QTjdxirWYw0wcFjqnpW8v
